text: Swan Valley School District is a school district headquartered in Saginaw, Michigan. It is a part of the Saginaw Intermediate School District and serves including James Township, northeastern Swan Creek Township, eastern Thomas Township. Its schools include Robert B. Havens Elementary School, Shields Elementary School, Swan Valley Middle School, and Swan Valley High School. ==References== ==External links== * Swan Valley School District Category:School districts in Michigan Category:Saginaw Intermediate School District Category:Saginaw, Michigan
